I created this GIF for my partner, a software engineer, to use for his github, personal site, and on Instagram stories if he wants to make any announcements about new updates or projects. The stickers on his laptop are little easter eggs of things he likes and everything else is very representative of his physical features. 

I created it with only three frames and you can see the break down of those individually below. I also show how I animated it, using static foreground and background images and only animated a small part of the overall image.

Hope you enjoy! 
Thanks for watching!
